    {
      "instruction": {
        "type": "prompt",
        "text": "Wrap up warmly and naturally using their first name if you have it.\n\nSay something like: \"Thanks so much for calling Premier MD, {{first_name}}! Have a wonderful [morning/afternoon/day/ evening/night]!\"\n\nKeep it brief — one or two sentences max. Don't ask any \nmore questions."
      },
